<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="344"><div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-left: 0"><tr valign="top"><td height="134"><div align="left"><font color="#339966"><font class="Helvetica13" face="Arial, Helvetica, adobe-helvetica, Arial Narrow" size="2">I have awoken my months of slumber. No, not really, I'v been busy, and have been working on our squadron website: http://www.nwocomp.n3.net I don't know what the futur holds for NWR, but I might be returning, who knows anymore. Being a webmaster by yourself is not easy. If I do return I will need an assistant. If I don't I will turn my website over to someone who is cabable, and trust&nbsp; worthy to carry the NWR name on. For now I say good-bye.</font></font></div></td></tr></div></table>
